                <div id="blurb">
                    <h1>San Francisco is in Crisis</h1>
                    <p>Real-estate speculators are evicting longtime city residents. Many of the affected are <strong>elderly</strong>, <strong>disabled</strong> and <strong>low-income</strong> with no affordable housing options. <strong>You can help</strong>. Don't rent or buy property available because of a no-fault eviction.
                    </p>

                    <div class="buttonContainer">
                        <p class="centered"><a href="#" class="CTA"><span class="hideMobile">Pledge to </span> Support Housing Justice</a></p>
